name: Registering as a user on the Utest.com website

testSteps.description: Given that Sergio is on the UTest Home page

children.description: Sergio open up
Sergio opens the U test page

testSteps.description:
When he enters all required registration fields
| firstName | lastName | email | birthMonth | birthDay | birthYear | postalCode | password | confirmPassword |
| Sergio | Suarez | ssuarez99@hotmail.com | March | 5 | 1993 | 170001 | Aguasmzl03 | Aguasmzl03 |

children.description: Sergio register
Sergio clicks on Button that shows us the form to register
Sergio enters 'Sergio' into where do we write the first name
Sergio enters 'Suarez' into where do we write the last name
Sergio enters 'ssuarez99@hotmail.com' into where do we write the email
Sergio select March on where do we select the birth Month
Sergio select 5 on where do we select the birth Day
Sergio select 1993 on where do we select the birth Year
Sergio clicks on Button that shows us the form to Next Location
Sergio enters '170001' into where do we write the zip or postal code
Sergio clicks on Button that shows us the form to Next Devices
Sergio clicks on Button that shows us the form to Next Last Step
Sergio enters 'Aguasmzl03' into where do we write the password
Sergio enters 'Aguasmzl03' into where do we write the confirm password
Sergio clicks on where do we approve the terms
Sergio clicks on where do we approve the policy
Sergio clicks on Button that shows us the form to Complete Setup

testSteps.description:
Then a UTest account is created
| textRegisterSuccess |
| First, please check your email inbox |

children.description: Then answer
